thread.title: Walter Yankowich
thread.title_full: Ace Rental Cars Australia & New Zealand reviewed by Walter Yankowich

author: Walter Yankowich
title: Walter Yankowich
text: During 15-day car rental in NZ, ACE was advised in advance the car would be returned 1-day early. Company gratefully accepted the early return but would not apply a refund/credit towards rental. Otherwise, good company for car rental.
